metadata.name: "The Christmas Carolers"
metadata.description:
As the guests of 'The Strangers at Casablanca' party mingle and enjoy the festive atmosphere, a peculiar group of carolers suddenly appears at the door. 

Dressed in mismatched, antique Christmas attire and wearing bizarre masks, they burst into the room with a cacophony of off-key singing. 

Despite their peculiar appearance and questionable musical talent, the carolers bring a touch of whimsy and unexpected cheer to the party, spreading holiday cheer and delighting the guests with their strange performance.
